import React from 'react'
import AppLayout from '../component/AppLayout'
import Head from 'next/head'

function signup() {
    return (
        <>
            <Head>
                <title> 회원가입</title>
            </Head>
            <AppLayout>
                회원가입
            </AppLayout>
        </>
    )
}

export default signup
